T26604 - Photo Deletion Confirmation Popup Not Displaying Properly in Portrait Mode
https://surveyjs.answerdesk.io/internal/ticket/details/T26604
***
To reproduce the issue, load the following JSON at https://surveyjs.io/create-free-survey.
```
{
  "pages": [
    {
      "name": "page1",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "file",
          "name": "question1",
          "needConfirmRemoveFile": true
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
