***
Follow these steps to reproduce the issue:
* Run [this demo](https://plnkr.co/edit/lodXlEnFRzP8chqt)
* Click a new page button within the page navigator (page2 - doesn't exist yet)

<img width="185" height="219" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8ed274e4-129f-4cf6-be57-68e96a62410c" />

* Enter a new page's title using on the design surface (using an inplace editor).

<img width="1039" height="562" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/ab3561bd-c004-40b7-aca6-f866d0177432" />

* The resultant survey JSON contains an expected extra page:
```
{
  "pages": [
    {
      "name": "page1",
      "title": "First Page",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "question1"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "page3",
      "title": "Second Page"
    },
    {
      "name": "page3",
      "title": "Second Page"
    }
  ],
  "headerView": "advanced"
}
```

