issue_body:
T24476 - [Logic Tab] : setValueExpression property is not getting updated/removed from JSON editor
https://surveyjs.answerdesk.io/internal/ticket/details/T24476
***
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps.
* Navigate to https://surveyjs.io/create-free-survey.
* Add two single-line text input fields.
* Activate the Logic tab.
* Setup the following logic rule which creates `setValueIf` and `setValueExpression` settings for `question2`.

<img width="419" height="493" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/33eebbab-b154-4e34-8f8c-a83446d1f573" />

* Remove the logic rule

**Issue:** The `setValueExpression` remains in a `question2`'s JSON:
```
{
  "pages": [
    {
      "name": "page1",
      "elements": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "question1"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "question2",
          "setValueExpression": "abc"
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
```
**Expected behavior:** `setValueExpression` is removed when a corresponding logic rule is removed.

